sk.stuba.fiit.perconik.eclipse.core.runtime

Class ForwardingPluginConsole

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.common.collect.ForwardingObject
      • sk.stuba.fiit.perconik.eclipse.core.runtime.ForwardingPluginConsole
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PluginConsole

    public abstract class ForwardingPluginConsole
extends com.google.common.collect.ForwardingObject
implements PluginConsole
    A plug-in console which forwards all its method calls to another plug-in console. Subclasses should override one or more methods to modify the behavior of the backing plugin console as desired per the decorator pattern.

    Note that this class does not forward the equals and hashCode methods through to the backing object. See ForwardingObject for more details.

    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Pavol Zbell
